   <fr:tree show-metadata="false" toc="false"><fr:frontmatter><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/jonmsterling.xml" title="Jon Sterling" addr="forest://erct/jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors><fr:date><fr:year>2023</fr:year><fr:month>12</fr:month><fr:day>31</fr:day></fr:date><fr:addr>forest://erct/erct-002Y/0</fr:addr><fr:route>http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-002Y/0.xml</fr:route><fr:title text="" /><fr:taxon>Proof</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter>
 <html:p>Fixing <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[b:B]]></fr:tex>, we must check that the <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001Q.xml" title="Fiber" addr="forest://erct/erct-001Q" type="local">fiber</fr:link> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f]]></fr:tex> over <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[b]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001H.xml" title="Contractible type" addr="forest://erct/erct-001H" type="local">contractible</fr:link>. For the centre of contraction, we must construct an element of this <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001Q.xml" title="Fiber" addr="forest://erct/erct-001Q" type="local">fiber</fr:link>; because <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001T.xml" title="n-truncated map" addr="forest://erct/erct-001T" type="local">propositional</fr:link> by <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-0048.xml" title="Embeddings are propositional" addr="forest://erct/erct-0048" type="local">Lemma <fr:contextual-number addr="forest://erct/erct-0048" /></fr:link>, the <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001Q.xml" title="Fiber" addr="forest://erct/erct-001Q" type="local">fiber</fr:link> is a <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001I.xml" title="Proposition" addr="forest://erct/erct-001I" type="local">proposition</fr:link>, so it suffices by the induction principle for <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-0028.xml" title="Propositional truncation" addr="forest://erct/erct-0028" type="local">propositional truncation</fr:link> to observe that the <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001Q.xml" title="Fiber" addr="forest://erct/erct-001Q" type="local">fiber</fr:link> is <html:em>inhabited</html:em> because <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-0029.xml" title="Surjection" addr="forest://erct/erct-0029" type="local">surjective</fr:link>.</html:p>
</fr:mainmatter></fr:tree>
 
