 <html:p>By <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-002Y.xml" title="Bijections are contractible" addr="forest://erct/erct-002Y" type="local">Lemma <fr:contextual-number addr="forest://erct/erct-002Y" /></fr:link>, <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-003F.xml" title="Bijection" addr="forest://erct/erct-003F" type="local">bijections</fr:link> are <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001T.xml" title="n-truncated map" addr="forest://erct/erct-001T" type="local">contractible</fr:link>; by <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-002H.xml" title="Contractible maps are biinvertible" addr="forest://erct/erct-002H" type="local">Corollary <fr:contextual-number addr="forest://erct/erct-002H" /></fr:link>, <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-003F.xml" title="Bijection" addr="forest://erct/erct-003F" type="local">bijections</fr:link> are <fr:link href="http://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/erct/erct-001T.xml" title="n-truncated map" addr="forest://erct/erct-001T" type="local">contractible</fr:link>.</html:p>
